    title: "Truck tailgate lift, scissor lift POWER PACK",
    category: "hydraulic",
    description: "POWER PACK Features &amp; Details",
    body: "<p>truck tailgate lift, scissor lift POWER PACK</p>\n<p>Hits: 1493</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Features &amp; Details</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Maintenance:</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Key Features</p>\n<p>Double Acting Hydraulic Pump</p>\n<p>POWER PACK --The electric hydraulic pump is a double-acting hydraulic pump, with strong power for lifting-up and lowering-down. Pumps are designed for long-lasting use, and reservoirs will not crack or leak even under harsh conditions.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Compact Structure</p>\n<p>The compact hydraulic power unit is consists of an electric motor, electromagnetic coil A/B ports with 3200 PSI Max relief setting on A port, and 1500 PS Max on B port, solenoid valves, 15ft control pendant, and a 6/10/12qt reservoir.</p>\n<p>Quick Start &amp; Oil Output of POWER PACK</p>\n<p>Connected to the 12V DC motor, our dump trailer hydraulic pump has 3.0KW max power, 2.0 GPM flow, 1.1 cc/r, and with duty lasting for 3 minutes for each start, featuring quick oil output and rapid starts each time.</p>\n<p>Versatile &amp; Convenient</p>\n<p>The 12V hydraulic pump comes with a 6/10/12qt metal cylinder tank, a pressure gauge, and 2 additional connectors for replacement. Its pendant control has 15ft (4.5 m) long and is designed with up-down buttons for easy use.</p>\n<p>Vertical/ Horizontal Mount</p>\n<p>The car-lift hydraulic power unit is designed for both horizontal and vertical mounts. It manifests impressive lifting and lowering capability. It can handle hydraulic work like lifting, pressuring, bending, straightening, tilting, and cutting.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Wide Application</p>\n<p>This power unit is widely used in stackers, small, and medium-sized lifting platforms. It is compatible with many dump trailers and movers and is a direct replacement for 12V DC remotely controlled hydraulic systems.</p>\n<p>6 Quart Double Acting Hydraulic Power Units with Hydraulic Gauge</p>\n<p>POWER PACK has unique features among the other hydraulic power unit on the market, has a powerful double-acting hydraulic cylinder pump, advanced brass pressure pump, and remote control, working excellent in lifting and pushing devices like dump trailer, lift gates, and tow trucks.</p>\n<p>POWER PACK Specifications</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-images\">\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-007.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-008.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-009.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-010.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-011.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-012.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-013.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-014.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-015.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-016.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-017.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-018.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n<img src=\"http://hyd.desanee.com/images/hfimag/powerpack/MHP-018.jpg\" alt=\"POWER PACK\" />\n</div>",
